	<p>To display the current command-line tool version, along with the platform and architecture, in a terminal run the <Ascua::Prism::Inline @language="shell" @code="surreal version" /> command without any further arguments.</p>
	<codes vertical>
		<Code @name="docs-cli-version-main.shell" text="Command line">
			user@localhost % surreal version
		</Code>
